item.title: CorpMates
item.description: Intro This is a small project I created along side my friend Clayton. I came up with the idea when more and more frequently I would login to the game EvE Online after long breaks and have people recognize me and I would have no idea who they were. To solve this issue I have created CorpMates, Simply type your name into the top box and either paste an individual or the entirety of the system into the second and hit submit.
